WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:02.800
Tongtong wait a minute

2
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.366
You don't have to say it.

3
00:00:07.866 --> 00:00:09.066
I won't forgive you.

4
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:11.800
Forgive who cares about your forgiveness

5
00:00:11.933 --> 00:00:13.466
It's you who did the wrong thing

6
00:00:13.466 --> 00:00:15.000
What are you talking about?

7
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:15.800
An Tong

8
00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:18.700
You wouldn't have known by now, would you?

9
00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:20.766
Where did I go wrong?

10
00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:22.433
You were abandoned by Gao Yu and committed suicide

11
00:00:22.533 --> 00:00:24.000
I ran to save you.

12
00:00:24.166 --> 00:00:25.333
Get justice for you

13
00:00:25.333 --> 00:00:27.166
I took you in when you had no place to live

14
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:28.300
Where did I go wrong?

15
00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:29.933
That's because you're sorry for me.

16
00:00:29.933 --> 00:00:31.366
That's why you helped me

17
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.500
I think you are seriously ill.

18
00:00:35.566 --> 00:00:36.900
guilty

19
00:00:37.966 --> 00:00:40.066
Why has Gao Yu treated me like this all these years?

20
00:00:40.666 --> 00:00:42.900
Didn't you tell him I had an abortion?

21
00:00:44.166 --> 00:00:47.166
That's why he looks down on me

22
00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:49.800
All my misfortunes are because of you

23
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:51.600
I told him this

24
00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:52.966
I want to help you.

25
00:00:52.966 --> 00:00:54.700
I want him to treat you well.

26
00:00:54.700 --> 00:00:56.600
Do you really want to help me?

27
00:00:57.533 --> 00:00:58.500
Over the years

28
00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:00.400
How many things have you done to me?

29
00:01:00.466 --> 00:01:02.700
An Tong, I hate you

30
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:04.766
I really hate you.

31
00:01:05.133 --> 00:01:06.666
I came to this point

32
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:09.300
All because of you

33
00:01:09.866 --> 00:01:11.100
It's my fault about Gao Yu

34
00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:11.600
I'm sorry.

35
00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:12.766
I apologize to you.

36
00:01:12.966 --> 00:01:14.066
In addition to that

37
00:01:14.333 --> 00:01:16.500
What else am I sorry for you?

38
00:01:16.766 --> 00:01:18.233
Do you still decorate?

39
00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:19.666
In college

40
00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:21.900
You clearly know that I like Xiaoyuke

41
00:01:22.266 --> 00:01:24.700
But it didn't take long for you to be with him

42
00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:28.566
Dare you say you didn't do it on purpose?

43
00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:29.866
How do you know?

